question: Tī MarS hō͘-su̍t kā hiān-chú-sî ê chhī-tiûⁿ kap siu-chiáⁿ ê chhī-tiûⁿ só͘ chò ê pí-kàu ê èng-iōng lāi-bīn, ū koan-hē ê hiān-chú-sî ê hong-hoat pí siáⁿ-mi̍h?
Siaⁿ-chi̍t-êAPK lia̍h-lâi kā tì-kàu 'generation' ia̍h-sī 'simulation' ê 'MarS' hong-hoat, ūi-tiāⁿ-chē hō͘?
Koh-iānn ê 'Detection' app-ia̍t, MarS hong-huat ē hōo 'Current Methods' lāi-bīn ê sî-kan-tè-píng ê hong-huat chóa-piàn án-tsuánn?
answer: 'Detection' lāi-bīn ê 'Current Methods' sī àn-tsōo gûn-kó͘ ê pí-kà, sī thàu-kue thiau-liám hiān-tsāi ê chhī-tiàm-bâⁿ (market_now) kah kó͘-thàu ê chhī-tiàm-bâⁿ (market_past) ê chha-khut. MarS hong-huat ē siau-tû tùi kó͘-thàu chu-liāu ê siau-hāu. Hō-iáⁿ, i sī pí kó͘-thàu ê chhī-tiàm-bâⁿ (market_now) kah tâng-sî sî-khì ê simu-market (simu-market_now), tùi sî-kan (hiān-tsāi vs. hit-ê sî-khì) ê pí-kà piàn-tsò sī chi̍t ê ki-tù-sī (si̍t-chāi vs. bô-si̍t-chāi) ê hong-khu.

question: Chiah-sī ūi-tio̍h 'MarS' hong-hoat sī chio̍h-chāi kóng-chò sī 'pipeline' ia̍h-sī ū 'generation' ê só͘-ū èng-iōng, lia̍t-chhut 'Jîn-chêng-chè chha-hng-hoat' ê lia̍t-pia̍k.
A khiat-bāng ê Iōng-tū (Application) tī 'Hiān-chí-sî Hoat-tō͘' (Current Methods) kah 'MarS' chi kan, chiap-la̍k-chiap-la̍k tùi lōe-iông pí-kàu piàn-chòe bô͘-gí pí-kàu, sī siáⁿ chi̍t khoán?
answer: Chhú-lí (Detection) chit khoán Iōng-tū (Application) sī chòe cheng-tōa ê pháiⁿ-sî-á ki-pún ê kái-piàn. Hiān-chí-sî ê hong-hoat oá-kè chi̍t ê le̍k-sú, thè-chi̍h khòaⁿ ê pí-kàu (Diff(market_now, market_past)). Siōng-tó-bái, MarS ê hong-hoat tùi chi̍t ê tâng-sî chûn-chāi ê bô͘-gí (simulated reality) lâi chòe pí-kàu (Diff(market_now, simu-market_now)). Chit ê tùi le̍k-sú ê ki-chún kái-piàn chòe bô͘-gí ê ki-chún lâi pí-kàu, sī chi̍t ê chin tiōng-iàu ê gîi-sik tē-khui, pí pa̍t ê hong-hoat kái-piàn tī piáu-koh lóng chin cheng-tōa.

question: Tī 'RL Environment' ê 'MarS' hong-hoat, kā 'Current Methods' ê su-liū khò-liāu ê chhà-pia̍t tòan-thok tì-sio, Nā-sī beh chò 'same application', chiah-ê siūⁿ-siōng ê MarS hong-hoat ē-iú nn̄g-ê te̍k-se̍k ē-tàng chha̍p chha̍p-chha̍p?
Siar 'RL Environment' che̍t-chiuⁿ ê sî-chūn, 'Current Methods' kap 'MarS' chi-kan, chū-liāu ê ū-hêng kap siang-tú-lu̍t ê chin-chiàⁿ-sèng ū siáⁿ-khoán cheng-chha?
answer: Chha-biat ê tiōng-tiám sī chū-liāu ê liōng kap siang-tú-lu̍t ê chin-chiàⁿ-sèng. 'Current Methods' oá-kò͘ 'hān-liōng ê chū-liāu' kap chi̍t-ê 'chà-phò͘' ê siang-tú-lu̍t (P(st+1|st,at)), chi̍t-pêng 'MarS' sī sú-iōng 'bōe-tiāⁿ ê chū-liāu' kap chi̍t-ê 'chin-chiàⁿ' ê siang-tú-lu̍t.

question: Lia̍h-sut ū kúi ê bô-kāng ê èng-iōng, i ê hong-hoat biâu-su̍t tiong ū 'data' chit ê sû, sī tī 'Current Methods' ia̍h-sī 'MarS' ê lē-piann?
Tùi chit-ê phiau-chún lâi kóng, MarS siâⁿ MarS kah bo̍k-chiân hong-hoat tùi-phîⁿ, te̍k-pia̍t sī tī chu-liāu kah chin-si̍t tāi-piáu hong-bīn ê bīn-cháⁿ tiâu-kiāⁿ, ū siáⁿ-mi̍h bīn-cháⁿ ê te̍k-tiám?
answer: Chit-ê chiâⁿ-thâu ê lí-liām sī kóng MarS hong-hoat beh chhiau-kòe le̍k-sú chiâⁿ-thâu í-ki̍k ū hān-chè ê chu-liāu ê hān-chè, iōng seng-seng kah bô͘-gí ki-chè ê hong-hoat lâi oân-seng. MarS tùi extrapolation kái chòe generation, tùi le̍k-sú phîng-kò kah chòe bô͘-gí phîng-kò, koh tùi ū hān-chè/chha-bó͘-ê chu-liāu bô͘-hêng kái chòe bô-hān/chin-chiàⁿ ê chu-liāu bô͘-hêng. Che sī hui-siông chiâⁿ-bī teh chhòng-chè koh-khah kiông-kò͘, koh-khah ún-teng, koh-khah chin-si̍t ê chu-liāu khoân-kéng lâi chòe hun-sek kah cheng-tiâng ha̍k-si̍p ê chiâⁿ-thâu chiáⁿ-thâu.

question: Tī chit ê phiau keh lāi, bô kā thâu hâng kā téng, ki-taⁿ ū kúi ê bô-kāng ê èng-iōng sī ū kái-su̍t ê?
Tī Forecasting ê khòaiⁿ-á, ēng siáⁿ-chiáⁿ ê hong-hoat?
